inners-writers-guild-america-1201705269/ |title=WGA Honors 'Big Short,' 'Spotlight,' 'Mad Men' at 68th Awards |work=Variety |first=Dave |last=McNary |date=February 13, 2016 |accessdate=February 13, 2016}}</ref>\n| [[Writers Guild of America Award for Television: Dramatic Series|Drama Series]]\n| ''Better Call Saul''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Writers Guild of America Award for Television: New Series|New Series]]\n| ''Better Call Saul''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Writers Guild of America Award for Television: Episodic Drama|Episodic Drama]]\n| [[Vince Gilligan]] and [[Peter Gould (writer)|Peter Gould]] (\"[[Uno (Better Call Saul)|Uno]]\")\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=4|[[20th Satellite Awards]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pressacademy.com/award_cat/2015/ |title=Satellite Awards (2015) |publisher=International Press Academy |accessdate=December 2, 2015 |date=December 1, 2015}}</ref>\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Television Series \u2013 Drama|Best Drama Series]]\n| ''Better Call Saul''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Actor \u2013 Television Series Drama|Best Actor in a Drama Series]]\n| Bob Odenkirk\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Series, Miniseries or Television Film|Best Supporting Actor in a Series, Miniseries or TV Film]]\n| Jonathan Banks\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Series, Miniseries or Television Film|Best Supporting Actress in a Series, Miniseries or TV Film]]\n| [[Rhea Seehorn]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2| [[32nd TCA Awards]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2016-tca-award-winners-people-917083/item/program-year-2016-tca-award-917081 |title='People v. O.J. Simpson' Tops 2016 TCA Award Winners |first=Lesley |last=Goldberg |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=August 6, 2016 |accessdate=August 7, 2016}}</ref>\n|Outstanding Achievement in Drama\n|''Better Call Saul''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Individual Achievement in Drama\n|Bob Odenkirk\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=4|